kimi-code-action
================

This project is derived from claude-code-action
(https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code-action), imported at upstream
commit 3e807ec379b815f9623b7ceca6c7f1f8585e9ead.

The upstream project is licensed under the MIT License.
See LICENSE for the full license text.

Substantial portions of the GitHub event handling, prompt generation, MCP
servers, and security hardening are adapted from the upstream project.
The model/CLI integration layer has been replaced to drive Kimi Code CLI
(https://github.com/MoonshotAI/kimi-code) instead of Claude Code.
